		<div id="comment_body_64408096"><p>perhaps having to give up what made your business worth existing is a sign that maybe you shouldn't be hundreds of thousands of employees big.   maybe it would be better for everyone, including the competitive economy, if such large companies just weren't allowed.</p></div>
	</div>

